Summary: About 8:20 pm travelling from NE to SW low and very fast bright light no sound
divs: Sighting DetailsSitting watching t.v inside my home. Happened to look out the window and a tear shaped light, bright with a darker middle. Like a LED light. It was low and traveling extremely fast. Faster than any plane could travel and lower than any comet. There was no tail and no sound. Flight pattern was NE to SW.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Swift Current
